"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-25-World-No-1-Sinner-withdraws-from-tennis-at-Paris-2024-due-to-illness-1vw1pmkOsog-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Jannik Sinner of Italy reacts in a men's singles quarterfinal match against Daniil Medvedev of Russia at the Wimbledon Championships at the All England Lawn Tennis and Croquet Club in London, United Kingdom, July 9, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 244, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9991290070039872, \"rank\": 0.0007751640393610407, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 303, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniil_Medvedev\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Daniil Medvedev\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniil_Medvedev\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniil_Medvedev\"}, {\"begin\": 322, \"end\": 328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9999879089290259, \"rank\": 9.012125051294948e-06, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 395, \"end\": 402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croquet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0197754967195454e-15, \"text\": \"Croquet\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croquet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croquet\"}, {\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9894941830354894, \"rank\": 0.010609966793311179, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9977317688280458, \"rank\": 0.0022731138343190255, \"text\": \"United Kingdom\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  Jannik Sinner has withdrawn from the Paris Summer Olympics due to tonsillitis, the world number one said on Wednesday, denting Italy's hopes of winning a first tennis medal at the Games since 1924.\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 455, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jannik_Sinner\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jannik Sinner\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jannik_Sinner\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jannik_Sinner\"}, {\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9991290070039872, \"rank\": 0.0007751640393610407, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sinner won his first Grand Slam title at the Australian Open earlier this year, and reached the semifinals of the French Open.\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 681, \"end\": 685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"score\": 0.9999999972237674, \"rank\": 2.7761676001122674e-09, \"text\": \"Slam\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grand_Slam_of_Curling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am saddened to inform you that unfortunately I will not be able to participate in the Paris Olympic Games,\\\" Sinner wrote in a post on X, formerly known as Twitter.\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"score\": 0.9999999999929514, \"rank\": 7.096035331051606e-12, \"text\": \"Twitter\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Twitter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After a good week of clay training I started to feel unwell.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I spent a couple of days resting and during a visit the doctor found tonsillitis and strongly advised me against playing,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sinner was also due to play in the men's doubles event alongside Lorenzo Musetti.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1227, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1211, \"end\": 1226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lorenzo Musetti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lorenzo_Musetti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will be replaced by 207th-ranked compatriot Andrea Vavassori.\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1292, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1275, \"end\": 1291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Vavassori\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrea Vavassori\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Vavassori\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Vavassori\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Missing the Games is a huge disappointment as it was one of my main goals for this season.\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1385, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I could not wait to have the honour of representing my country in this very important event.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Good luck to all the Italian athletes who I will support from home,\\\" Sinner concluded.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1500, \"end\": 1507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"score\": 0.8625229858038148, \"rank\": 0.159115798115673, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sinner's withdrawal means world number two and 24-time Grand Slam champion Novak Djokovic will now be the top seed in the men's singles draw.\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1642, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novak Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sinner became the latest among a number of tennis players to withdraw from the competition, with the Czech Republic's Olympic silver medalist Marketa Vondrousova and Poland's Hubert Hurkacz pulling out on Monday.\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1922, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1817, \"end\": 1825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9993134535062966, \"rank\": 0.0006